item.description: Introduction I respectfully submit this online portfolio to support my application for tenure and promotion to the rank of Associate Professor in the Department of Mathematics and Statistics at Winona State University. This is in accordance with the requirements of the IFO/MnSCU Master Agreement, Article 22: Professional Development and Evaluation, and Article 25: Tenure, Promotion, and Non-Renewal. The Math-Stat crew of 2016-2017 listens with rapt attention
